WEBVTT

00:07.710 --> 00:08.940
<i>Calm down, Wally.</i>

00:08.980 --> 00:11.325
<i>Get away from me!
You don't tell me what to do!</i>

00:11.365 --> 00:13.430
<i>I tell you what to do!</i>
I pay your salary!

00:13.470 --> 00:16.625
–Calm down, Wally. Alright? Take it easy!
–Do you know who I am?

00:16.665 --> 00:18.767
–I’ll tell you who I am!
–I said, calm down, Wally.

00:18.807 --> 00:21.740
–Jenna? What's going on?
–Get out of here, sir!

00:21.780 --> 00:23.815
–I said get the hell out!
–He's my neighbor.

00:23.855 --> 00:25.855
An attorney. What's she being charged with?

00:25.895 --> 00:27.370
Prostitution.
Now stay out of this. Okay?

00:27.410 --> 00:30.970
You'll all pay!
I'm State Senator Wally Bird,

00:31.150 --> 00:33.415
you'll be meter maids by this time
tomorrow, you Keystone Cops,

00:33.455 --> 00:36.307
I'll screw you all!

00:36.342 --> 00:39.125
I'll screw each and every one of you,

00:39.160 --> 00:41.450
I'll screw your mothers!
–Wally!

00:41.830 --> 00:44.575
I'm State Senator… Wally… Bird…!

00:44.610 --> 00:47.646
–He must be a wonderful lover.
–Get off of me!

00:48.070 --> 00:50.005
I'm… Wally… Bird.

